00:10:36,879 --> 00:10:37,760
<i>Christmas morning.</i>

247
00:10:39,920 --> 00:10:42,719
<i>That was the last time</i>
<i>I ever saw her.</i>

248
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:45,720
Hey, don't forget
to buy yourself
something from me.

249
00:10:45,800 --> 00:10:47,799
<i>That night,</i>
<i>the police found my mom's car</i>

250
00:10:47,880 --> 00:10:50,839
<i>abandoned and empty,</i>
<i>except for her glasses,</i>

251
00:10:50,920 --> 00:10:53,279
<i>and a single</i>
<i>wrapped gift for me.</i>

252
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:55,799
<i>So I put on my mom's glasses</i>

253
00:10:55,879 --> 00:10:57,799
<i>and vowed I wouldn't</i>
<i>open her gift</i>

254
00:10:57,880 --> 00:10:58,919
<i>until I found her.</i>

255
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:01,040
<i>But I felt so guilty</i>

256
00:11:01,119 --> 00:11:02,320
<i>that it was my mystery solving</i>

257
00:11:02,400 --> 00:11:03,960
<i>that had caused her</i>
<i>to go missing,</i>

258
00:11:04,040 --> 00:11:07,439
<i>I started having</i>
<i>horrifying hallucinations.</i>

259
00:11:07,520 --> 00:11:09,879
