265
00:11:24,879 --> 00:11:26,040
Wow. After hearing that,

266
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:27,559
I not only feel
emotionally hooked,

267
00:11:27,640 --> 00:11:29,840
I understand the stakes
of your journey, Velma.

268
00:11:29,919 --> 00:11:31,880
You remembered my name.

269
00:11:31,959 --> 00:11:34,000
Huh? That's never happened
to me before.

270
00:11:35,399 --> 00:11:37,079
Fred! Watch out!

271
00:11:37,159 --> 00:11:38,839
You're right! If anyone ever
saw me talking to you,
I'd die of shame.

272
00:11:44,719 --> 00:11:45,719
Velma!

273
00:11:45,799 --> 00:11:46,679
There you are!

274
00:11:46,759 --> 00:11:48,159
Norville? What the hell?

275
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:50,160
