Voice mails.

276
00:11:50,239 --> 00:11:51,920
And then my dad heard me
call you the B word,

277
00:11:51,999 --> 00:11:53,440
so I lost my phone
for 24 hours.

278
00:11:53,519 --> 00:11:54,999
But I had to find you

279
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:56,480
because I still didn't know
if you'd listened to my VMs,

280
00:11:56,559 --> 00:11:58,159
