our math homework together.

282
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:02,360
Just email me
your answers like always.

283
00:12:02,439 --> 00:12:03,600
Yes, of course.

284
00:12:03,679 --> 00:12:04,919
Though I left you
some other VMs, voice--

285
00:12:04,999 --> 00:12:07,160
I know what VMs are!
Get to the point.

286
00:12:07,239 --> 00:12:08,280
I already did.

287
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:10,759
In my VMs.

288
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:11,960
<i> Velma,</i>

289
00:12:12,039 --> 00:12:13,239
<i>it's Norville. From math.</i>

290
00:12:13,320 --> 00:12:14,599
<i>I know who killed Brenda.</i>

291
00:12:14,680 --> 00:12:15,960
