292
00:12:16,040 --> 00:12:17,440
I left you six more VMs.

293
00:12:19,559 --> 00:12:22,439
<i>So I guess what I'm saying is,</i>
<i>I don't know who killed Brenda.</i>

294
00:12:22,520 --> 00:12:24,280
Damn it, Norville,
you're wasting my time.

295
00:12:24,359 --> 00:12:27,600
If I can't convince people
I didn't kill Brenda
by tomorrow,

296
00:12:27,679 --> 00:12:28,919
I'm going to be arrested.

297
00:12:28,999 --> 00:12:30,239
I know, But I also know
how to find out

298
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:31,479
who did kill Brenda.

299
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:33,159
Have you ever wondered
why Spooner's,

300
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:35,719
a boring malt shop
owned by a woman
with a "breathe" tattoo,

301
00:12:35,800 --> 00:12:37,559
