for group projects.

408
00:17:05,880 --> 00:17:08,080
But last night, we spoke.

409
00:17:08,160 --> 00:17:09,720
And yes, while it was awful,

410
00:17:09,800 --> 00:17:12,919
I learned this is
not a creature
capable of murder. Nay.

411
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:16,520
It is just a scared little boy
who wants our friendship.

412
00:17:29,440 --> 00:17:30,879
Perfect.

413
00:17:33,960 --> 00:17:37,120
Well, well, well.

414
00:17:39,359 --> 00:17:40,960
Well, well, well.

415
00:17:57,720 --> 00:18:00,560
-Well, well, well.
-Look, whatever this is,
