00:18:30,320 --> 00:18:32,120
Yeah, we've all heard
those rumors.

433
00:18:32,199 --> 00:18:34,440
Anyway, Fred's
so self-conscious
about his body,

434
00:18:34,519 --> 00:18:37,679
