out of the bathroom
at Spooner's Malt Shop

435
00:18:37,760 --> 00:18:39,360
when he has to use it.

436
00:18:39,439 --> 00:18:41,280
So have fun with that.

437
00:18:41,359 --> 00:18:44,279
