and maybe it's healthy if I--

442
00:18:51,279 --> 00:18:52,440
No time!
Drive me to Fred's house!

443
00:18:52,520 --> 00:18:53,879
I'll get my windbreaker.

444
00:18:57,959 --> 00:18:59,400
Why would Fred kill Brenda

445
00:18:59,479 --> 00:19:01,399
just because
she photographed him
in the bathroom?

446
00:19:01,480 --> 00:19:02,359
