just to get away with it.

449
00:19:05,799 --> 00:19:07,839
But won't looking for my camera
trigger your potentially
fatal hallucinations?

450
00:19:07,920 --> 00:19:09,160
Though
"Saving Friend from Death"

451
00:19:09,239 --> 00:19:10,879
