for a great college essay.

452
00:19:10,960 --> 00:19:12,600
My hallucinations have stopped.

453
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:14,480
Once I realized
solving mysteries

454
00:19:14,559 --> 00:19:16,079
didn't cause
my mom to go missing,

455
00:19:16,160 --> 00:19:18,040
