that triggered them.

456
00:19:18,119 --> 00:19:19,840
Okay, but have you given
any thought

457
00:19:19,919 --> 00:19:21,999
to all the other ways
you could die trying
to solve a mystery?

458
00:19:22,079 --> 00:19:24,159
Crushed by
a revolving bookcase?

459
00:19:24,240 --> 00:19:25,119
Attacked by bats.

460
00:19:25,200 --> 00:19:26,199
Falling off a fence.

461
00:19:26,280 --> 00:19:27,280
Stop. I'll be fine.

462
00:19:28,880 --> 00:19:30,280
