463
00:19:30,359 --> 00:19:32,639
No, I'm cool
and graceful like a swan.

464
00:19:32,720 --> 00:19:34,960
Okay, 'cause it really
sounded like you fell.

465
00:19:48,360 --> 00:19:49,239
What?

466
00:19:49,320 --> 00:19:50,680
I'm bored.

467
00:19:50,759 --> 00:19:52,600
Norville! Get off my jock
and let me solve this mystery.

468
00:19:56,239 --> 00:19:57,879
Oh. God,
I'm starting to hallucinate.

469
00:19:57,960 --> 00:19:59,640
<i>You just said those were over.</i>

470
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:01,759
Well, I guess I needed
more than three minutes online

471
00:20:01,840 --> 00:20:04,199
to make a mental health
diagnosis, didn't I?

472
00:20:05,319 --> 00:20:06,720
Wait. This isn't so bad.

473
00:20:06,799 --> 00:20:09,119
No, it's not bad, Velma.

474
00:20:09,200 --> 00:20:11,319
But it's going to be!

475
00:20:12,360 --> 00:20:13,239
Help me, Norville!

476
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:19,159
<i>Velma! Velma! Can you hear me?</i>

477
00:20:19,240 --> 00:20:21,519
<i>Just remember,</i>
<i>these hallucinations</i>
<i>are only in your head,</i>

478
00:20:21,599 --> 00:20:22,920
<i>so focus on what I'm saying.</i>

479
00:20:22,999 --> 00:20:24,600
Velma!

480
00:20:24,680 --> 00:20:26,760
Velma.

481
00:20:26,839 --> 00:20:28,800
You're not
saying anything.

482
00:20:28,879 --> 00:20:31,879
<i>I know! I'm, uh,</i>
<i>kind of drawing</i>
<i>a blank right now.</i>

483
00:20:34,119 --> 00:20:36,080
<i>Have you seen</i>
<i>any good movies lately?</i>

484
00:20:36,159 --> 00:20:38,320
Oh, God.
Here comes the big one.

485
00:20:38,400 --> 00:20:39,800
<i>Stop! You can't die.</i>

486
00:20:39,879 --> 00:20:42,079
Why? I'm weird
and no one likes me.

487
00:20:42,160 --> 00:20:43,080
That's not true.

488
00:20:43,880 --> 00:20:45,280
I like you.

489
00:20:45,359 --> 00:20:47,200
Like, like like you.

490
00:20:47,279 --> 00:20:48,320
- Wait, what?
- Velma.

491
00:20:48,399 --> 00:20:49,599
No, you don't.

492
00:20:49,680 --> 00:20:51,760
You're like a brother to me.
That's hilarious.

493
00:20:54,200 --> 00:20:55,639
